<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title><%= title %> - OpenID Connect Example</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #e74c3c;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #e74c3c;
            margin-top: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .error-container {
            background-color: #fff0f0;
            border-left: 4px solid #e74c3c;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 3px;
        }

        .error-details {
            margin-top: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        pre {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            overflow-x: auto;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>Error Occurred</h1>

<div class="error-container">
    <h2><%= error %></h2>
    <p><%= error_description %></p>
</div>

<div class="error-details">
    <h3>What this means</h3>
    <p>There was a problem during the authentication process. This could be due to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>You denied permission on the consent screen</li>
        <li>The authorization server encountered an error</li>
        <li>The session expired or was invalidated</li>
        <li>There was a configuration issue with the client</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<a href="/" class="btn">Return to Home</a>
</body>
</html>